ea127b124d2fbf31db8.mp4?t=1749477145\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Details</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will get 1 common chest drop every <strong>3 hours</strong> and 1 rare chest every <strong>18 hours</strong><br></li><li>You can freely <strong>sell chests</strong> on community market, <strong>trade</strong> them or<strong> open in game</strong>. Most of them are <strong>free</strong> to open, but <strong>rarest</strong> one requires <strong>keys</strong> which you can get from items shop or buying DLC<br></li><li>You can <strong>trade up</strong> 9 items of the same rarity for 1 with increased rarity<br></li><li>You can use hamsters in game as models<br></li><li>Game has leaderboards for best collectors with maximum amount of hamsters<br></li><li>You can easily get achievements just for clicking</li></ul>",
